lead_paragraph: Pau Gasol had season highs with 21 points and six assists, and the San Antonio Spurs snapped a three-game home losing streak with a 96-86 victory over the Detroit Pistons on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Gasol's Season-High 21 Points Help Spurs End Home Skid
